{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83e\udde1 A GAME CREATED BY THE COZY COMMUNITY, FOR THE COZY COMMUNITY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>charming</strong> RPG where you'll discover the joys of running your own <strong>cozy cafe</strong> in a <strong>pixel-perfect world</strong>. From brewing the perfect cup of coffee to making friends with the locals, <strong>experience a blend of relaxation and adventure during your own coffee break.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922570/extras/IntroductionTailsideSteamB.gif?t=1738141276\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u2615\ufe0f PREPARE COFFEE </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Master</strong> the <strong>art of coffee-making</strong> as you fulfill various coffee orders:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf31 Prepare different types of coffee </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf31 Unlock new options through upgrades </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922570/extras/TailsideCoffeeMakingSteamB.gif?t=1738141276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83c\udfa8 DECORATE THE CAFE </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Personalize</strong> every corner of your cafe to <strong>your own unique taste</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf31 Fully customizable cafe </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf31 Different decoration categories </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922570/extras/TailsideDecoratingSteamB.gif?t=1738141276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udc65 MEET VILLAGERS </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet <strong>cute villagers</strong> that will <strong>help you</strong> through out your journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragr